The paper focuses on image clustering and classification using hypergraph learning frameworks and regression models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as sparse representation and collaborative representation, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with multimedia data, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper addresses the issue of image clustering and classification, which can be considered as a sub-topic of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
